---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contáctenos"
  description="Póngase en contacto con SmartCheck Costa Rica para solicitar una inspección vehicular o para cualquier consulta relacionada con nuestros servicios."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background with gradient -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-smartcheck-blue via-smartcheck-blue/90 to-smartcheck-blue/80 z-0"></div>
    
    <!-- Decorative elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-smartcheck-accent/10 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-white/10 rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">ESTAMOS PARA AYUDARLE</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Contacto
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Estamos a su disposición para responder cualquier pregunta sobre nuestros servicios de inspección vehicular
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <!-- Contact Info -->
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-smartcheck-blue mb-6">Información de Contacto</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-10">
              Comuníquese con nosotros a través de cualquiera de estos medios o complete el formulario y le responderemos a la brevedad.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <!-- Phone -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Teléfono</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">+506 8675 2713</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Lunes a Viernes: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Email -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Correo Electrónico</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">smartcheckcr@gmail.com</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Respuesta en 24 horas o menos</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Location -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Ubicación</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">San José, Costa Rica</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Servicio a domicilio en toda el área metropolitana</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Social Media -->
            <div class="mt-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Síguenos en Redes Sociales</h3>
              <div class="flex gap-3">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/smartcheckcr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-smartcheck-blue hover:bg-smartcheck-blue hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/smartcheckcr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-smartcheck-blue hover:bg-smartcheck-blue hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772A4.902 4.902 0 015.45 2.525c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465C8.901 2.013 9.256 2 11.685 2h.63zm-.081 1.802h-.468c-2.456 0-2.784.011-3.807.058-.975.045-1.504.207-1.857.344-.467.182-.8.398-1.15.748-.35.35-.566.683-.748 1.15-.137.353-.3.882-.344 1.857-.047 1.023-.058 1.351-.058 3.807v.468c0 2.456.011 2.784.058 3.807.045.975.207 1.504.344 1.857.182.466.399.8.748 1.15.35.35.683.566 1.15.748.353.137.882.3 1.857.344 1.054.048 1.37.058 4.041.058h.08c2.597 0 2.917-.01 3.96-.058.976-.045 1.505-.207 1.858-.344.466-.182.8-.398 1.15-.748.35-.35.566-.683.748-1.15.137-.353.3-.882.344-1.857.048-1.055.058-1.37.058-4.041v-.08c0-2.597-.01-2.917-.058-3.96-.045-.976-.207-1.505-.344-1.858a3.097 3.097 0 00-.748-1.15 3.098 3.098 0 00-1.15-.748c-.353-.137-.882-.3-1.857-.344-1.023-.047-1.351-.058-3.807-.058zM12 6.865a5.135 5.135 0 110 10.27 5.135 5.135 0 010-10.27zm0 1.802a3.333 3.333 0 100 6.666 3.333 3.333 0 000-6.666zm5.338-3.205a1.2 1.2 0 110 2.4 1.2 1.2 0 010-2.4z" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@smartcheckcr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-smartcheck-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-smartcheck-blue hover:bg-smartcheck-blue hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M19.59 6.69a4.83 4.83 0 0 1-3.77-4.25V2h-3.45v13.67a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-5.2 1.74 2.89 2.89 0 0 1 2.31-4.64 2.93 2.93 0 0 1 .88.13V9.4a6.84 6.84 0 0 0-1-.05A6.33 6.33 0 0 0 5 20.1a6.34 6.34 0 0 0 10.86-4.43v-7a8.16 8.16 0 0 0 4.77 1.52v-3.4a4.85 4.85 0 0 1-1-.1z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Form -->
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-smartcheck-blue mb-6">Envíenos un mensaje</h2>
              
              <form class="space-y-6">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <!-- Nombre -->
                  <div>
                    <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre Completo</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-smartcheck-blue focus:border-transparent" placeholder="Su nombre completo" required>
                  </div>
                  
                  <!-- Email -->
                  <div>
                    <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Correo Electrónico</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-smartcheck-blue focus:border-transparent" placeholder="Su correo electrónico" required>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Teléfono -->
                <div>
                  <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Teléfono</label>
                  <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-smartcheck-blue focus:border-transparent" placeholder="8888-8888" required>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Servicio -->
                <div>
                  <label for="service" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Servicio de Interés</label>
                  <select id="service" name="service" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-smartcheck-blue focus:border-transparent" required>
                    <option value="" selected disabled>Seleccione un servicio</option>
                    <option value="inspeccion-estandar">Inspección Estándar</option>
                    <option value="inspeccion-premium">Inspección Premium</option>
                    <option value="inspeccion-corporativa">Inspección Corporativa</option>
                    <option value="otro">Otro</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Mensaje -->
                <div>
                  <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Mensaje</label>
                  <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-smartcheck-blue focus:border-transparent" placeholder="¿Cómo podemos ayudarle?" required></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Submit Button -->
                <div>
                  <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-smartcheck-blue hover:bg-smartcheck-blue/90 text-white font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                    Enviar Mensaje
                  </button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Nuestra Cobertura</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Brindamos servicio a domicilio en toda el área metropolitana de Costa Rica.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
        <div class="aspect-video">
          <!-- Placeholder for map - in production use Google Maps or other map provider -->
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center p-8">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-gray-400 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Mapa de Cobertura</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500">En este espacio se mostraría un mapa interactivo con nuestra área de cobertura.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Preguntas Frecuentes</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Respuestas a las preguntas más comunes sobre nuestros servicios de contacto.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
            <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-smartcheck-blue pr-8">
                ¿Cuál es el tiempo de respuesta a mi consulta?
              </h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="px-6 pb-5">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Respondemos a todas las consultas en un plazo máximo de 24 horas laborales. Para solicitudes urgentes, recomendamos contactarnos directamente por teléfono.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
            <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-smartcheck-blue pr-8">
                ¿Cómo puedo agendar una inspección?
              </h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="px-6 pb-5">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Puede agendar una inspección a través de nuestro formulario de contacto, llamándonos directamente o enviándonos un email. Le responderemos para confirmar la fecha y hora según su disponibilidad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
            <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-smartcheck-blue pr-8">
                ¿Cuáles son las zonas de cobertura para las inspecciones?
              </h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-smartcheck-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="px-6 pb-5">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Brindamos servicio a domicilio en toda el área metropolitana de Costa Rica, incluyendo San José, Heredia, Alajuela y Cartago. Para otras zonas, por favor contáctenos para verificar disponibilidad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/preguntas-frecuentes" class="inline-flex items-center text-smartcheck-blue hover:text-smartcheck-accent font-medium">
          Ver todas las preguntas frecuentes
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout> 